MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

98-449. State ex rel. LTV Steel Co. v. Conrad.

In Mandamus and Procedendo. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for writs of mandamus and procedendo. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
